@{b}About Connect 4@{ub}

Connect 4 is a brand new version of this classic game for your desktop. It features
a MUI interface, a Player Address Book to store names and player types, a handy
turn indicator and the best graphics in any game of the same genre I've been able
to find on Aminet.

See the section "Usage" to find out how to play!


@{b}Requirements@{ub}

MUI 3.8 and Lamp.mcc

@endnode

